{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_51_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 手作りスタンプラリー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、新しい服がほしいって言ってたでしょ？\nここで見ていったらどうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you wanted some new clothes‚  right‚  sis?\nHow about we take a look around here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.0866665523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "って、あれ……？\nお、お姉ちゃん、なんで泣いてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…?\nS-sis‚  why are you crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8194502667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5151934307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "だって千紗が、私のために編集部の人達に連絡して……\nスタンプラリーまで、手作りしてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Chisa… contacted the magazine editors for me…\nAnd you even handmade this stamp rally…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "一生懸命、頑張ってくれたんだって思うと\nそれだけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think about how hard you worked for me‚\njust that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2900682927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、千紗。何かほしいものはない？\nお姉ちゃんが買ってあげる。新しい服がいいかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚  Chisa. Do you want anything?\nI’ll buy it for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4083676499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん落ち着いて。お誕生日なんだから\nお姉ちゃんがほしいものを買わなきゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-calm down‚  sis. It’s your birthday‚\nso you should buy what you want!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5333336194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.7492532573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あそこのお店なんてどうかな。お姉ちゃん\n綺麗だし、ああいう大人っぽい服も似合いそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! How about that store over there?\nSince you’re pretty‚  sis‚  I think those mature-looking clothes would suit you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9159200034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4191398783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかしら\nふふ、綺麗だなんて、もぉ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really?\nFufu‚  you think I’m pretty? Honestly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6877154746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6679820541
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.56
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　その隣の服って……\nとっても可愛いわね。ちょっと試着してみようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? That outfit next to it…\nIt’s so cute! Maybe I’ll try it on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9653515654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3396190806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、少し待っててくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚  can you wait for me a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3396190806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9115463498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ？　お姉ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Sis?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9115463498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3137250902
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.3333376885
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ\nふふ、気に入ったからそのまま買ってきちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m back.\nFufu‚  I liked it so much that I bought it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3333376885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2481248698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしら、せっかくのお誕生日企画だし\n少しだけ気合いを入れてみたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do I look? Since it’s a special birthday project‚\nI tried to dress up a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7000053724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4361308259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4361308259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8437427284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん！　髪型、とっても可愛いと思う！\n服は……お、同じようなの、持ってた気もするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah! I think your hairstyle is super cute!\nThe clothes… Um‚  I feel like you already have something similar…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4666720391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.4768716576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう、千紗\n最近お仕事が忙しくて、買いに来る時間がなかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚  thank you‚  Chisa.\nI’ve been so busy with work that I haven’t had time to go shopping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6959419968
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.766673565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、そろそろ次の場所に行きましょうか\n次は、『遊園地』ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚  shall we head to the next location?\nThe next one is “Amusement Park”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.766673565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、普段は繋がりのない場所が繋がっていく\nやっぱりスタンプラリーはいいわね、わくわくしちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haah~‚  normally unrelated places are being connected like this…\nstamp rallies are the best. They make me so excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8102054895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8775295975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……お洋服、私が選んであげた方が良かった\nのかなぁ……。嬉しそうだし、いいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-ahaha… Maybe I should have chosen the clothes for you….\nI’m glad you like it‚  but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 131.4304526093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "一個目のスタンプの形、アルファベットの『H』に\n見えるわね。二箇所目は『O』……何かの暗号かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first stamp looks like the letter “H”.\nThe second one looks like “O”… I wonder if it’s some kind of code?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1000068983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、スタンプラリー、楽しんでくれてるみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚  I’m glad you’re enjoying the stamp rally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2217972519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、それは最後のお楽しみだよ\nそれよりほら、遊園地に着いたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll find out at the end‚  sis!\nLook‚  we’re here at the amusement park!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7348016186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……二人で来るのはいつぶりかしら\nあのメリーゴーラウンド、昔一緒に乗ったわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… It’s been a while since we’ve been here together.\nWe rode that merry-go-round together a long time ago‚  right?",
        "id": ""
      },
