    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗の頑張り屋な部分が、こんなところで……\nもう、やるしかっ……いやー！？　いきなり来たー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚  your stubborn streak… at a time like this…\nI have no choice but to… Kyaaaah!? It suddenly appeared!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.7000130021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 330.4819842263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム、楽しかったね。お姉ちゃん\n一生懸命頑張ってて、映画の主人公みたいだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That game was fun‚  wasn’t it‚  sis?\nYou were working so hard‚  you looked like the protagonist of the movie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 334.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "最後の方なんて、「いくぜー！」とか「いかせてもら\nいやすぜー！」って叫んで、凄く気合いが入ってたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Toward the end‚  you were yelling things like “Let’s go!” and “Take this!”\nYou were so fired up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.9707312191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "あれは、もう、振り切るしかなかったから……\nでも、そうね、楽しかったわ。ありがとう、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just had to… give it my all…\nBut‚  yeah‚  it was fun. Thanks‚  Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.6333381974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、じゃあ三つ目のスタンプを押すね\nカードに……ぽんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚  okay‚  here’s the third stamp.\nOnto your card… Stamp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 362.8666776343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
